<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhēn xī jīn tiān 迦南126</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shī qù duō shǎo gè jīn tiān, bù zhī dào qù zhēn xī,
 zhēn hòu huǐ, wǒ duō xiǎng zài dào tuì jǐ suì,
 kě shí guāng yǐ jīng zǒu guò bù zài fù fǎn,
 guāng yīn yī qù yǒng bù huí,
 cǐ shí wǒ miàn xiàng lán tiān, miàn xiàng bái yún zhǎng tàn!
 ràng guò qù de wú zhī yú mèi suí fēng piāo yuǎn,
 wǒ yào bǎ wò zhe jīn tiān měi yī fēn měi yī miǎo
 ràng tā zhēn zhèng shǎn yào chū xī wàng de guāng diǎn,
 ràng shén lái zhǐ yǐn, bǎ zhì huì míng dēng diǎn rán
 zhī dào zài rén shēng de lù shàng zhēn xī jīn tiān.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>126</hymn_number>
</song>